    <prp:previousProposals>Sahai is PI on one Cycle 0 and two Cycle 1 ALMA highly-graded proposals related to studies of pre-planetary nebulae. The data from the Cycle 0 proposal (2011.0.00510.S) have been published (Sahai et al. 2013, ApJ, 777,62). Partial data from 2012.1.00501.S has been received and presented at conference "Revolution in Astronomy with ALMA", Dec 8-11, 2014; a paper is under preparation. No data from the Cycle 1 proposal 2012.1.00678.S) has been received as yet.</prp:previousProposals>
